### 2.7 Generation progress in chat

Avatar generation is async (1-5 min). Handle gracefully:

1. Agent calls generate_avatar tool
2. Tool starts HeyGen job, immediately returns { status: 'generating', jobId }
3. Agent responds in chat: "Started avatar generation. This takes 2-4 minutes.
   I'll notify you when it's ready. You can keep working on other scenes."
4. Server polls HeyGen every 15 seconds
5. When complete: SSE event to frontend:
   { type: 'avatar_ready', sceneId, layerId, videoUrl }
6. Frontend shows notification in chat:
   "✓ Avatar ready — Scene 2 updated"
7. Scene HTML regenerates, preview reloads

