## PART 4 — AI IMAGE GENERATION + STICKERS

### 4.1 Models supported

Multiple models via their APIs or fal.ai as a unified gateway:

```ts
type ImageModel =
  | 'flux-1.1-pro'        // fal.ai — highest quality, slowest
  | 'flux-schnell'        // fal.ai — fast, good quality
  | 'ideogram-v3'         // fal.ai — great for text in images
  | 'recraft-v3'          // fal.ai — best for illustrations/icons
  | 'stable-diffusion-3'  // fal.ai — versatile
  | 'dall-e-3'            // OpenAI — reliable, safe
```

Model selection guide (injected into agent):
- Photo-realistic: flux-1.1-pro
- Fast iteration: flux-schnell
- Contains text/labels: ideogram-v3
- Illustration/diagram style: recraft-v3
- General purpose: stable-diffusion-3

